---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro"; import EnquiryForm from "../../components/EnquiryForm.astro"; import { ASSETS, BRAND } from "../../data/site";
---
<BaseLayout title="Enquire about a Fox franchise" description="Submit a dedicated Fox Mowing & Gardening franchise opportunity and territory enquiry."><section class="form-hero section-black"><div class="container form-layout"><div class="form-intro"><span class="eyebrow">Franchise enquiries</span><h1>Explore your place in the Fox network.</h1><p>Share your preferred region, timing and goals with the franchise team. This dedicated pathway is separate from customer service enquiries.</p><div class="form-points"><span>✓ Region and territory interest</span><span>✓ Business goals and timeframe</span><span>✓ No commitment created by enquiring</span></div><a class="text-link" href={`mailto:${BRAND.email}`}>Questions? {BRAND.email}</a></div><EnquiryForm kind="franchise" /></div></section><section class="section-pad section-soft"><div class="container narrow"><h2>A considered commercial decision</h2><p>Territory availability, costs, obligations and fit require direct discussion and formal documentation. Website content and this enquiry are introductory only.</p><img class="form-support-image" src={ASSETS.franchisees} alt="Fox franchise team" width="1200" height="600" loading="lazy"/></div></section></BaseLayout>

